# Keep this file small and temporary.
# Rules:
# 1) Add only reviewed false positives or accepted risks.
# 2) Every entry must include: owner, reason, created date, expiry date.
# 3) Remove entries as soon as a patch is available.
#
# Format:
# CVE-YYYY-NNNNN # owner=@team reason="..." created=YYYY-MM-DD expires=YYYY-MM-DD
#
# Example:
# CVE-2025-12345 # owner=@backend reason="False positive in test-only path" created=2026-02-22 expires=2026-03-15

